{"type":"message","id":"7896568a","parentId":"12330be6","timestamp":"2026-03-26T05:47:04.006Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是关于学习法语和英语的周期问题。这是一个比较个人化的问题，取决于多种因素。但我没有用户的\"计划\"具体内容，不知道他们的学习目标、每周投入时间、当前水平等。\n\n让我先检查一下是否有相关的记忆/上下文可以帮助了解用户的学习计划。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5lchc8fydxib_1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"法语 英语 学习计划 周期"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":24397,"output":88,"cacheRead":6269,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30754,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774504018311}}
